<plot>Experyment6 takes a whimsical look at how some of the other Planets in our Solar System might view the shortcomings of Humanity. The character, M, a powerful hidden presence surrounding Earth, is in the hot seat. The experiment he began nearly a Century ago is failing according to these Planets. M's experiment, Humanity itself, is given a hard deadline-the year 2080-by the concerned Planets. Hanging in the delicate balance with their imposed deadline is nothing less than the continued existence of all Humanity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185686</url></doc>
